---
title: Asian Fusion Beef Tacos with Creamy Slaw & Crispy Shallots
description: Tacos with Asian flavours are coming together to make an unbeatable fusion of flavours. It’s packing tortillas with oyster sauce-glazed beef strips, adding a colourful slaw and sprinkling crispy shallots for a bit of crunch. It’s the ultimate combination!
